  "body": "[Testing for events today](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/master/test/crowdsale/Crowdsale.test.js#L86-L91) -- [is kind of a pain](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/master/test/helpers/expectEvent.js).\r\n\r\nIt'd be really nice if I could do something like the following:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nconst eventGenerator = myContract.EventName({});\r\ntry {\r\n  await myContract.someFunctionThatProducesEvent();\r\n  let expectedEvent = await eventGenerator.next();\r\n} finally {\r\n  eventGenerator.close(); // if only JS had a `using` pattern :-(\r\n}\r\n```",
